    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "You can communicate with the node via a script that keeps the miner disabled unless there are pending transactions. See the answer here: https://ethereum.stackexchange.com/questions/3151/how-to-make-miner-to-mine-only-when-there-are-pending-transactions/3152#3152\r\n\r\nSave the script as a JS file and run:\r\n\r\n```console\r\n./build/bin/geth --datadir clique-data --preload mine.js attach\r\n```",
